snippet.title: Amber Heard and Johnny Depp: The Truth Revealed
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp

Amber Heard has issued multiple accusations against Johnny Depp, which have had an extremely detrimental effect on his career.

As it turns out however, she herself might have been guilty of everything she accused him of.

Full podcast this excerpt is lifted from:
https://youtu.be/irMrwOMfhfg
